" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;良好的编码习惯，会定期总结自己在工作中遇到的各种问题和解决方案。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:6.6500pt;" ><td width=750  valign=center  style="width:450.0000pt;padding:0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:3.7500pt;" ><td width=750  valign=center  style="width:450.0000pt;padding:0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=MsoNormal  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=800  valign=center  style="width:480.0000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><table class=MsoNormalTable  align=center  style="border-collapse:collapse;width:450.0000pt;margin-left:20.4000pt;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr><td width=750  valign=center  style="width:450.000